          <h2>Text & Inline Elements</h2>
          <p>This paragraph shows <strong>strong</strong>, <em>emphasis</em>, <mark>highlighted text</mark>, <small>small print</small>, and an inline <code>code</code> sample. Here's an abbreviation: <abbr title="HyperText Markup Language">HTML</abbr>.</p>

          <p>Quotations: <q cite="https://example.com">This is a short inline quote</q>. Block quote follows:</p>
          <blockquote cite="https://example.com">
            <p>"Education is the most powerful weapon which you can use to change the world." — <cite>Nelson Mandela</cite></p>
          </blockquote>

          <h3>Lists</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Unordered list item</li>
